<Base
  title="The End of the App Layer: Why MCP Changes Everything About AI Governance — KYDE"
  description="MCP lets AI agents connect directly to enterprise systems — bypassing the application layer that was always the implicit governance control point. Most enterprises haven't noticed yet."
