                Kyde Witness governs not just LLM calls but every tool your agents invoke — including MCP servers. Every call is intercepted, attributed to an agent identity, checked against role-based scope, and written into a tamper-evident audit trail. The app layer disappears. The governance layer doesn't.
              </p>
